Uses of Package
org.sbml.squeezer

Packages that use org.sbml.squeezer
org.sbml.squeezer This is the core of SBMLsqueezer as it contains the central classes for reaction type analysis, kineticl law generation and some specialized exceptions. 
org.sbml.squeezer.gui This package contains all necessary classes for the graphical user interface. 
org.sbml.squeezer.kinetics This package contains one class for each supported kinetic law. 
 

Classes in org.sbml.squeezer used by org.sbml.squeezer
CfgKeys
          This is a list of possible command line options and configuration of SBMLsqueezer.
LawListener
          Classes that implement this interface can display the progress made by KineticLawGenerator when assigning BasicKineticLaw, Parameter, UnitDefinition objects and so forth to a model.
RateLawNotApplicableException
          An exception to be thrown if the selected kinetics is not applicable to the given reaction.
ReactionType
          The purpose of this class is to analyze a reaction object for several properties, such as the number of reactants and products, the types of modifiers and their number, if the stoichiometries are always integer numbers or real valued and much more.
 

Classes in org.sbml.squeezer used by org.sbml.squeezer.gui
KineticLawGenerator
          This class identifies and generates the missing kinetic laws for a the selected model in the given plug-in.
LawListener
          Classes that implement this interface can display the progress made by KineticLawGenerator when assigning BasicKineticLaw, Parameter, UnitDefinition objects and so forth to a model.
RateLawNotApplicableException
          An exception to be thrown if the selected kinetics is not applicable to the given reaction.
SBMLsqueezer
          The main program of SBMLsqueezer.
